➜武汉光谷万豪酒店任命总经理——陈文峰先生
http://www.sohu.com/a/435704257_100116241	1951
<p>近期，万豪国际集团正式任命陈文峰（Steven Chen）先生担任武汉光谷万豪酒店总经理，全面负责酒店的运营管理及战略发展。</p>
<p>Recently, Marriott International officially appointed Mr. Steven Chen as General Manager of Wuhan Marriott Hotel Optics Valley. He will be in charge of hotel overall operation and development.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201202/271942fdf15a4eacacd5faf715d785ef.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>陈文峰先生拥有近20年酒店从业及国际酒店高层管理经验，曾先后在万豪、温德姆、洲际、新濠集团等国际品牌酒店担任要职。在此次履新之前，陈文峰于厦门万丽度假酒店担任总经理一职。</p>
<p>Steven has nearly 20 years working experience in hospitality industry. He has served Marriott International, Wyndham, IHG Hotels, and Melco International etc. Before taking his new position, he was General Manager of Renaissance Xiamen Resort &amp; Spa.</p>
<p>作为资深的酒店管理者，以及对万豪品牌文化的深入了解，陈文峰先生拥有非凡的领导力、洞察力以及对酒店行业独到的见解，相信在他的带领下，武汉光谷万豪酒店将继续创造卓越的客户体验和经营业绩，为武汉光谷高端消费注入全新的活力，并成为行业佼佼者。</p>
<p>As a professional hotelier, and in depth understanding of Marriott culture, Steven will lead the team of Wuhan Marriott Hotel Optics Valley to continuously be outstanding in the marketing and achieving more success and providing exceptional experience for each guest and delivering new energy in Wuhan Optics with his excellent management concept.</p>